  <sect1>
    <title>Network Requirements</title>
    <formalpara>
      <title>Network Infrastructure</title>
      <para>During &susemgr; Setup the following network requirements must be met or in place. <itemizedlist>
          <listitem>
            <para>IP Address, Netmask, and Gateway</para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN)</para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>DNS server resolvable both via DNS and reverse lookup</para>
          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>A proxy server should be setup to access the external network (when required)
                <emphasis>NTLM is currently not supported</emphasis> Your firewall should allow
              access to the following (http and https URLs) <itemizedlist>
                <listitem>
                  <para>nu.novell.com</para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                  <para>secure-www.novell.com</para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                  <para>update.novell.com</para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                  <para>scc.suse.com</para>
                </listitem>
                <listitem>
                  <para>updates.suse.com</para>
                </listitem>
              </itemizedlist></para>
          </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
      </para>
    </formalpara>

